data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spans 1,894 square feet of pure elegance, nestled on a sprawling 5-acre oasis. Embrace the perfect blend of modern luxury and natural serenity as you explore the open-concept living spaces bathed in natural light. Indulge in the spacious master suite, offering a tranquil escape with a luxurious ensuite bath. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms provide flexibility for guests or a home office. Outside, the expansive 5 acres beckon, offering a canvas for your outdoor dreams - from gardening to recreational activities, the possibilities are endless.  This residence embodies the essence of a private sanctuary, creating an unparalleled lifestyle where sophistication meets nature. Don't miss the chance to make this extraordinary property your forever home. Schedule a showing and let the magic of this 5-acre haven captivate you!
